data.title: Collection Search
data.meta_description: The Jersey Heritage Archive & Online Collections section allows you to subscribe to view scanned copies of archives such as the German Occupation Registration Cards and important document transcriptions online.
data.text:
Suggested record(s) that relate to this item:

D/S/A/4/A4547

One, or more, of the following conditions apply (see ‘Access restrictions’ above for more details):

• A digital copy is available to view online with a subscription or to purchase

• The record is exempt from public access under the Freedom of Information (Jersey) Law 2011

• The record is closed under the Data Protection (Jersey) Law 2018

• The record is closed for preservation due to fragile physical condition of original document

For further information or to make a request for access please email us.
